oogle 下<br />\n<br />\n多數都係唔會燒熱個鑊 擺塊扒落去先開獲 皮向下 細火<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無錯 望各位巴打指導"},{"pid":"b53d8a23976f8de0599718a0543d98e9da3c7925","tid":494350,"uid":99582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返過幾個月廚房仔 啲炸雞翼係會灯左先炸  煎既我就唔知得唔得</blockquote><br />\n有人教係煎到靚靚仔仔 之後拎去叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f62e8f0cc6ef91ff7b57641722752420be7f74","tid":494350,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbbb8ddf0be0b6bdc9564665426ad03fef3f733b","tid":494350,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返過幾個月廚房仔 啲炸雞翼係會灯左先炸  煎既我就唔知得唔得</blockquote><br />\n有人教係煎到靚靚仔仔 之後拎去叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解整唔到你個名咁</blockquote><br />\n個名要類似url咁 好似打網址 要有一點"},{"pid":"47fe564b8a26696abd0b473c11c8e11d19d14658","tid":494350,"uid":133050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"插支溫度計入個雞度 焗爐開低溫焗到165f <br />\n再用cast iron pan 開最大火煎 幾下<br />\n<br />\n要脆仲有好多辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea71ebf71e08afb7787e5aad0bc2650f2d2fb524","tid":494350,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>插支溫度計入個雞度 焗爐開低溫焗到165f <br />\n再用cast iron pan 開最大火煎 幾下<br />\n<br />\n要脆仲有好多辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔用焗爐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eee474893ae355e19ae3413cecf13f4528c998e","tid":494350,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"煲熟左先煎,好似呢條片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wSqTkgYvbPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwSqTkgYvbPQ&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b2f832fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wSqTkgYvbPQ</a>"},{"pid":"a7c48c19c5ce6628b03f8697b11f64ac5a76a976","tid":494350,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:17:09.000Z","msg":"煎完 囉去焗 蒸 叮"},{"pid":"895043660690b75e422ab4f0409ff379ae46d9c1","tid":494350,"uid":157510,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"先煎皮至金黃<br />\n<br />\n之後先再轉底<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就可以鎖住肉汁,做到外脆內嫩既效果"},{"pid":"b3d4a70d546e11bffa86ad4faaecd13d88a54f84","tid":494350,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"要脆的話要用紙抹乾表皮的水份或者風乾一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c763464b625885aaf7dd6d003084893b44dfb4f","tid":494350,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a5d81788527413ab2fa1ba98de36a7fc778df40","tid":494350,"uid":74981,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TXXXuBkX7QY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTXXXuBkX7QY&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a2b86332\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TXXXuBkX7QY</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e30654fc1d2838793b0d35c7ce347ed109016c","tid":494350,"uid":119720,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"我自己係大火兩邊快煎三十秒左右（煎到金黃），然後放少少水入鑊（浸住三份一塊雞扒咁上下）。之後蓋住個鑊等佢蒸煎，到啲水乾哂就得。<br />\n<br />\n同日式煎餃子煮法差唔多，外脆內嫩有肉汁。<br />\n<br />\n記得唔好切/𠝹塊雞，雞翼都係咁整。"},{"pid":"99940d274f22159ceb43fa751dc81602ce9fd198","tid":494350,"uid":62993,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"雞扒要先處理，用刀切斷根或用捶打爛纖維，咁樣食落亦會相對易咬，切斷根令雞扒煎時唔會收縮，保持比較大嘅表面面積，受熱均勻，另外，注意雞扒厚度是否平均，若果有地方厚左就用刀剖開，令厚度平均，確保均勻受熱，煎前吸乾水份，再用簡單的鹽、胡椒粉淹一下（新鮮雞扒），就可以落鍋。<br />\n未開火前把雞放落鍋，我細火將雞油迫出，迫出後用中猛火煎香，直至雞皮煎至微微焦黃，便可反面，轉小火鍋蓋上鍋蓋燜熟，正常厚度同手掌大size應該8-10分中即可。<br />\n可利用牙籤拮入最厚地方大約三秒，再放上上唇測驗是否熱，大概有你熱水煲熱水溫度應該就熟，再擔心嘅可以切開最厚地方/中心睇下。<br />\n熟左之後倒走鍋內多餘油份，將雞皮反至鍋面，中猛火烘脆雞皮，咁做亦可以迫走多餘油份，入口無咁油膩，上碟後可按個人口味加入調味粉/醬汁。"},{"pid":"cb42d274292089b61101622094eb0e149d89845b","tid":494350,"uid":968,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/TXXXuBkX7QY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTXXXuBkX7QY&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a2b86332\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TXXXuBkX7QY</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你煎一塊都廿幾分鐘就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf79ec60569d7ae3d68d411d47aa6f95186e07b","tid":494350,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:15:36.000Z","msg":"上粉煎"},{"pid":"c08fc92df945a8872cd9c1b8b832eeda047fffda","tid":494350,"uid":29120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:25:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61483bf715914d19d6b1b5486ae8ca323f600695","tid":494350,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:35:13.000Z","msg":"起鑊用蒜頭 薑 蔥<br />\n<br />\n煎到咁上下 就快熟 就開大啲個火快速將個皮變乾 入面唔會太熟 反轉又煎下<br />\n<br />\n熄火 個熱力被脆皮封住出唔到來 本來就快熟嘅入面會慢慢熟 外脆內嫰<br />\n<br />\n9up但你可以認真思考下 我母親會煮 太夜了遲啲幫you問一問"},{"pid":"755df6bac26967c00cbc825f768806c40b97b08b","tid":494350,"uid":31773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出面用焗爐架<br />\n一係就要大火 等佢內外鬥快熟<br />\n用細火出面熟曬入面都仲係生</blockquote><br />\n今晚啱啱焗咗雞翼，正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用大火先會唔熟<br />\n<br />\n根本雞翼就係要慢火煎<br />\n<br />\n而要脆口可以茶少量生粉慢火剪<br />\n<br />\n或者用焗爐焗完再大火快煎"},{"pid":"832b08a6bfd1ebf9f5c097bc5aaa4fdcfd4bfdad","tid":494350,"uid":108078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底洗唔洗加水冚蓋?"},{"pid":"702d0b726e647cb852cb8fbe1410354066d7aec7","tid":494350,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:01:20.000Z","msg":"蒸熟吸走 D水再炸"},{"pid":"8d928c9015f6cb64d63cfcec666ec8beda2cd05c","tid":494350,"uid":138557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"好肚餓啊屌"},{"pid":"69b5a4bf232c40cf50cecfcc4545825322637201","tid":494350,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"煎到咁上下要熄火 &quot;o琴&quot; 蓋焗2,3分鐘"},{"pid":"626cb9bb5f2261bfc10e3e4163825aa289983f01","tid":494350,"uid":142479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:58:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/78g7PK03Ayg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F78g7PK03Ayg&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=05ceb35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/78g7PK03Ayg</a><br />\n可以參考下台灣既教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ce15a856c10946a9e52f3a4339d1d8ab256008","tid":494350,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:02:18.000Z","msg":"慢煮機 再煎"},{"pid":"a682a57f070f354fc49d75a731392792f663607c","tid":494350,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:39:21.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"1cb47dda21f17ad4df585a3b43960e2596a0f24c","tid":494350,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T21:47:15.000Z","msg":"我近排無聊試下 <br />\n用焗左嘅雞 放一晚雪<br />\n之後另一日拎出嚟<br />\n落油 大火 前皮個面先 時間自己控制下<br />\n<br />\n仲有前之前 放d鹽先<br />\n整完幾似古野家<br />\n女朋友都話ok <br />\n你試下，我都教左d frd話ok<br />\n<br />\n利申，亂咁整整到"},{"pid":"35c85d2085a620c917ea92b7297c2a67aa78de19","tid":494350,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:28:13.000Z","msg":"其實就咁放隻雞扒 利用佢自己流出黎既油<br />\n用細火煎佢20-25分鐘 中間反下 落下鹽/其他調味料<br />\n就會做到皮脆內嫩<br />\n<br />\n利﹕由細到大鳩煮經驗"},{"pid":"f801f850f5a3f469319fff712dfc827cac453c4a","tid":494350,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實就咁放隻雞扒 利用佢自己流出黎既油<br />\n用細火煎佢<span style=\"color: red;\">15-20分鐘</span> 中間反下 落下鹽/其他調味料<br />\n就會做到皮脆內嫩<br />\n<br />\n利﹕由細到大鳩煮經驗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係自己睇情況 無計開時 應該無20-25咁耐"},{"pid":"e3b2674baed2d32a8420bf682007d55934ef5456","tid":494350,"uid":138725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:31:12.000Z","msg":"雞扒搽胡椒鹽橄欖油 放rosemary<br />\n入保鮮袋 用飲管抽真空<br />\n煲60度熱水 keep住60度煮45mins<br />\n煮完 燒紅煎pan 放油放蒜<br />\n冒煙時放雞扒 每邊煎到脆<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"7adb176346deab5c74ada478465276a104989c0b","tid":494350,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:34:54.000Z","msg":"雞扒就咁煎成日唔熟<br />\n最後要放焗爐<br />\n一係就放棄塊皮   煎到熟"},{"pid":"3854391d76ce0fd81df2b95ebb8d712bfe622f1d","tid":494350,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T23:04:27.000Z","msg":"滾滾佢再煎香兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d896829cb03772ad098892ba4497f6731d1151a","tid":494350,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"sous vide"},{"pid":"df372c8f1f1e1daedae543341ce6228bcd61795c","tid":494350,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T23:35:21.000Z"